Welcome to Dunbar Golf Tours, 
 
 

		 
		 

Specialists in tailor made golf holidays in Ireland, Scotland and a host of other destinations, Dunbar Golf Tours Ltd is a family company with over ten years experience in the golf travel industry.  

The most important thing to us... is you, our client and our focus is on providing you with a golfing holiday that will live forever in the memory. We listen to your requirements and deliver an experience that will exceed your expectations in every department from service through to value for money.  

So whether you are planning a golf intensive trip with the guys or a more romantic sojourn with your loved ones and featuring as much sightseeing as golf, we look forward to assisting you.  

Marc Dunbar 
Managing Director
 
		
		 
 
  


 
 
 
 
 

  

 
 
  
	 
	 
	 
	 
	 
	 
	 
	 
 
 

 
 
 
  
